00:18:19,020 --> 00:18:19,620
 ovdje te ne znamo,

211
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:21,980
 ovdje možeš malo primat

212
00:18:21,980 --> 00:18:23,240
 više te ljudske ljubavi,

213
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,900
 tih lajkova i tako dalje.

214
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:25,840
 Onda šta se...

215
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:27,000
 Onda ova žena koja je bila

