379
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:13,560
 Ljubavi prema Bogu.

380
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:14,380
 I pazi evo

381
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:15,800
 dolazi mi još

382
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:16,140
 ova stvar

383
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:16,740
 da ti je kažem.

384
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:18,360
 Mnogi ljudi mišle

385
00:22:18,360 --> 00:22:20,220
 da je prepreka

386
00:22:20,220 --> 00:22:21,220
 između njih i Boga

387
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:22,520
 i sad dok sluša

388
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:23,100
 evo zjevaju

389
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:23,600
 i spavaju.

390
00:22:23,740 --> 00:22:24,860
 Kad se govori o ljubavi prema Bogu

391
00:22:24,860 --> 00:22:25,340
 mnogi ljudi

392
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:26,560
 ma koja je ljubav prema Bogu?

393
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,180
 Šta ovaj govori?

394
00:22:27,180 --> 00:22:28,840
 I neki od vas

395
00:22:28,840 --> 00:22:29,720
 ste mi čak to i rekli.

396
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:31,220
 Da je to nerealno.

397
00:22:31,220 --> 00:22:32,240
 Zašto stalno govorimo o tome?

398
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,440
 Neki danas koji ste tu

399
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,120
 ste mi to rekli.

400
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,580
 Se nasmijao i pustio sam.

401
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,720
 Nemoj ljudima govoriti

402
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,380
 da ih Bog ljubi.

403
00:22:37,380 --> 00:22:39,360
 Mnogi misle

404
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:40,660
 da je prepreka

405
00:22:40,660 --> 00:22:41,580
 između nas

406
00:22:41,580 --> 00:22:42,400
 i toga da živimo

407
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,100
 u Božoj ljubavi

408
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:44,920
 trpljenje u svijetu.

409
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,240
 Nemoj mi govoriti

410
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:46,760
 da je Bog ljubi

411
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,660
 kad dijete može boliti

412
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:48,040
 od raka.

413
00:22:48,040 --> 00:22:49,340
 Nemoj mi to govoriti.

414
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:50,880
 Ali to nije prava prepreka

415
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:51,660
 između tebe i Boga.

416
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:52,800
 Prava prepreka

417
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:53,600
 između tebe i Boga

418
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,540
 je tvoja ljubav

419
00:22:54,540 --> 00:22:55,240
 prema tamih.

420
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,220
 Da nisi iznio

421
00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:57,420
 kad se to dogodi

422
00:22:57,420 --> 00:22:58,420
 kad se dogodi obraćenje

423
00:22:58,420 --> 00:22:59,380
 da ja iznesem

424
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:00,200
 moje

425
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,000
 zlo pred Boga

426
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,080
 moju tamu pred Boga

427
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:04,060
 moje laži pred Boga

428
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:05,600
 kad se upali moje srce

429
00:23:05,600 --> 00:23:07,120
 potpuno drugačije

430
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:08,320
 gledam na trpljenje u svijetu.

431
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:10,020
 Pošlijem ga gledati

432
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,500
 kao jedan poziv

433
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:13,100
 da ne živi za sebe.

434
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:14,320
 Potpuno drugačije.

435
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:15,260
 Gledam ga s očima

436
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:15,980
 po niznosti.

437
00:23:15,980 --> 00:23:17,820
 Potpuno drugačije.

438
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:18,500
 To sam doživio

439
00:23:18,500 --> 00:23:20,000
 i toliko ljude znam

440
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,180
 koji to doživljavaju.

441
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,480
 Potpuno drugačije.

442
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:24,720
 Zamisli da nema trpljenja

443
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:26,020
 u ovom našem

444
00:23:26,020 --> 00:23:28,040
 idolatrijskom stanju uma

445
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:30,000
 u kojem naš um je

446
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:30,980
 tvornica idola

447
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:32,180
 tvornica lažnih bogova

448
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:33,100
 tvornica iluzija

449
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:34,060
 jer ne možemo prihvati

450
00:23:34,060 --> 00:23:34,840
 stvarnost da smo

451
00:23:34,840 --> 00:23:35,700
 u dubini sami

452
00:23:35,700 --> 00:23:37,300
 i da je život isprazan

453
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:38,140
 i da dolazi smrt

454
00:23:38,140 --> 00:23:39,660
 i da sve što radim

455
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:40,720
 je na kraju bezvrijedno.

456
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:42,460
 Bez Boga, naravno.

457
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:43,560
 Ako ga nemam,

458
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:44,560
 bezvrijedno je.

459
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:47,600
 I u ovom našem stanju

460
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:49,060
 uma čovječanstva

461
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:49,660
 u kojem smo

462
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:50,920
 tvornice idola

463
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,380
 radimo i proizvodimo laži

464
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:53,940
 zamisli da nema trpljenja.

465
00:23:53,940 --> 00:23:56,320
 Kaže

466
00:23:56,320 --> 00:23:57,980
 Bog Katarini Sijenskoj

467
00:23:57,980 --> 00:23:59,500
 ma u sve trpljenje

468
00:23:59,500 --> 00:24:00,240
 u sve boli

469
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:00,840
 u smrt

470
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:01,820
 u sve bolesti

471
00:24:01,820 --> 00:24:03,780
 vi opet grlite ovaj svijet

472
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:04,980
 kao da ste stvoreni za njega

473
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:06,260
 kao da samo njega želite.

474
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:07,880
 A zamisli da nema trpljenja.

475
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,720
 Postali bi neki,

476
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:09,880
 ne znam da li se sjećate

477
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:10,820
 onih teletabisa.

478
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:12,380
 Tako bi ljudi bili

479
00:24:12,380 --> 00:24:13,300
 neki teletabisi,

480
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:16,060
 neka površna

481
00:24:16,060 --> 00:24:16,920
 ili neki praščići,

482
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:17,160
 ne znam,

483
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:19,200
 bili bi kao neke svinjice

484
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,140
 koji uživaju,

485
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:20,420
 ne znam,

486
00:24:20,420 --> 00:24:21,160
 u malo blata.

487
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:23,380
 Mi koji smo stvoreni

488
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:23,900
 za svetost,

489
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:24,960
 koji smo stvoreni za Boga.

490
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:26,220
 Bože,

491
00:24:26,220 --> 00:24:26,780
 hvala ti,

492
00:24:26,780 --> 00:24:28,040
 možeš li to i hvala?

493
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:28,640
 Hvala ti za trpljenja,

494
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:29,940
 ne razumijem ih puno puta,

495
00:24:29,940 --> 00:24:30,600
 niti ih želim,

496
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:31,400
 niti ih zazivam.

497
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:33,080
 Na ikoga,

498
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:34,120
 pa ni na sebe.

499
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:35,680
 Ali činjenica je,

500
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:36,840
 to sam ono,

501
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:38,680
 čitao sam onaj tekst,

502
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,440
 prokleto,

503
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:39,880
 ljubljen.

504
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,860
 Kad sam ja otkrio

505
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:43,780
 koliko su važna trpljenja

506
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:44,560
 u mojom životu,

507
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:46,320
 su me vodila Bogu,

508
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:47,520
 jer su raskrinkavale meni.

509
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:48,740
 Onda je o danas jako važno.

510
00:24:48,740 --> 00:24:50,080
 Zašto jedna osoba

511
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:50,520
 ne ljubi Boga?

512
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:51,260
 Zaključujem s tim.

513
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:52,580
 Zašto jedan čovjek

514
00:24:52,580 --> 00:24:53,160
 ne ljubi Boga?

515
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:55,880
 Samo jedan je odgovor.

516
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,660
 Jer svoje grijehe

517
00:24:57,660 --> 00:24:59,220
 ne iznosi van pred njega.

518
00:24:59,220 --> 00:25:02,140
 Zašto ti ne ljubiš Boga?

519
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:03,200
 Zašto ti je srce hladno?

520
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,860
 Zašto nemaš potrebu za molitvom?

521
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:06,220
 Zašto ne žudiš priče,

522
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:06,860
 sti ispovjed,

523
00:25:06,860 --> 00:25:07,920
 nego to samo reda radi,

524
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:08,480
 obavljaš?

525
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:11,240
 Ili kad moliš um ti stalno luta,

526
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,860
 to je znak da ne ljubiš Boga.

527
00:25:12,860 --> 00:25:15,660
 Druga postoje napasti u molitvi,

528
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:17,460
 ali ne možeš se koncentrirati,

529
00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:18,420
 ne možeš biti...

530
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,040
 Šta to znači?

531
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,060
 Znači da ga ne voliš.

532
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:22,100
 Kad si s nekim koga voliš,

533
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:23,440
 ne luta ti um negdje drugdje.

534
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,680
 Tu si s njim.

535
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:27,140
 Da koji je način?

536
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,940
 A pomozite nam,

537
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:29,800
 kažeš,

538
00:25:29,800 --> 00:25:30,960
 časni pomozite nam,

539
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:31,860
 kako ćemo ljubiti Boga?

540
00:25:31,860 --> 00:25:33,520
 Evo potičen tvoj duh,

541
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:34,580
 to mora se dogoditi čudo,

542
00:25:34,580 --> 00:25:37,260
 to je nemoj više skriva svoj tamu,

543
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:38,120
 iznesi je van.

544
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:40,160
 Prije svega,

545
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,080
 pred njim,

546
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:41,900
 idi pred njega.

547
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:43,340
 Budi gol pred njim.

548
00:25:43,340 --> 00:25:43,920
 To je odmor.

549
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:45,500
 Bit pred Bogom ono što jesi.

550
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:46,800
 Napokon se možeš odmoriti.

551
00:25:46,800 --> 00:25:48,680
 Stalno smo u napetosti.

552
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,240
 Znate, jedan od težih poslova

553
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,400
 koje ljudi rade je gluma.

554
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:53,020
 Zato što mnogi glumci piju.

555
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:54,840
 Toliko te zamori.

556
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:56,140
 A mi smo svi glumci.

557
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:57,380
 Toliko to umara.

558
00:25:57,380 --> 00:25:58,120
 Toliko umara.

559
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,840
 Mislim koja divota kad otkriješ.

560
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:01,760
 Može biti gol pred Bogom.

561
00:26:01,760 --> 00:26:02,460
 Može biti što jesi.

562
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:03,120
 On te ljubi.

563
00:26:04,220 --> 00:26:05,220
 Onda imamo ispovjed.

564
00:26:05,220 --> 00:26:07,380
 Daš na jednu dobru ispovjed.

565
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:08,480
 Kažeš sve.

566
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:10,900
 Koliko od vas nikad niste se raskrinkali

567
00:26:10,900 --> 00:26:12,100
 u ispovjedi.

568
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:12,660
 Nikad.

569
00:26:12,660 --> 00:26:13,760
 A to je divno.

570
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:14,400
 To je divota.

571
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:17,800
 Može se upaliti u tebi napokon.

572
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,600
 da možeš početi ljubiti Boga.

573
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:20,980
 Svim umom.

574
00:26:20,980 --> 00:26:21,580
 Svim srcem.

575
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,340
 Svim silama.

576
00:26:22,340 --> 00:26:23,500
 Evo tu je život.

577
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:26,220
 Izvan toga je tama iluzija.

578
00:26:26,220 --> 00:26:27,980
 Evo onda završavam s time.

579
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:28,620
 Ljubi Boga.

580
00:26:28,620 --> 00:26:29,640
 I živjet ćeš.

581
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,460
 Evo ljubi lažne bogove.

582
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:33,400
 I lagano ćeš umirat.

583
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:36,180
 U teškim mukama možemo tako.

584
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:37,280
 Ljudi su u teškim mukama.

585
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:38,280
 Zbog toga ne ljubia Boga.

586
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:40,340
 Slušavaju umjetravno težu u svoj život.

587
00:26:40,340 --> 00:26:41,420
 S malo više sporta.

588
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:42,340
 S malo više zdrave hrane.

589
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:42,800
 S malo više.

590
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:43,680
 Ali nikako.

591
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,780
 Nikako taj balans.

592
00:26:44,780 --> 00:26:47,200
 Evo ono što je kraljestvo Božje.

593
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,940
 Mir i radost.

594
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:49,280
 I pravenstvo duhu sve tome.

595
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:51,420
 Evo kad počnemo ljubiti istinu.

596
00:26:51,420 --> 00:26:52,000
 Ljubiti Boga.

597
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,000
 Koji je divan.

598
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,260
 Koji nas je objavio u svom sinu Isusu Hristu.

599
00:26:55,260 --> 00:26:56,000
 Ljubeći nas.

600
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:56,920
 Skriža.

601
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:57,960
 Kad smo ga razapinjali.

602
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,620
 Ta ljubav je uskrsla.

603
00:26:59,620 --> 00:27:00,160
 Vječna.

604
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,780
 Jedino što naš život vadi.

605
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:10,480
 Hvala.

